# UICP – External Verification Package (Phases 1‑5)

## What this package contains

This package provides public interfaces and automated verification scripts
for all five phases of the UICP constraint integrity pipeline. It allows
independent engineers and AI labs to confirm every claim made by the system
without accessing any internal algorithms, pipeline logic, or design maps.

